  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/ec8695e1d9b5434be54011110df371bb.poster.avif?t=1774345525\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/ec8695e1d9b5434be54011110df371bb.webm?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/ec8695e1d9b5434be54011110df371bb.mp4?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Sometimes, to remember who you were, you must walk through worlds that never existed.\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You wake up. Around you — emptiness.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You don’t know who you are.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You feel no pain.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You feel no body.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You are nothing but a skull. Empty, like your heart. Oh, right — you don’t have a heart. Yo-ho-ho-ho-ho.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/e9e485ddc4d340fa77a6aa0fe0f7b919.poster.avif?t=1774345525\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/e9e485ddc4d340fa77a6aa0fe0f7b919.webm?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/e9e485ddc4d340fa77a6aa0fe0f7b919.mp4?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Empty Skull</u></strong> is an atmospheric indie adventure puzzle game where you explore mysterious dimensions, strange creatures, fragments of lost memories... and voices that may exist only in your head.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you dive deeper into the worlds between worlds, you begin to realize: you are here for a reason.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/3371a79f5d7b0a0515dfd6cfbed283a5.poster.avif?t=1774345525\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/3371a79f5d7b0a0515dfd6cfbed283a5.webm?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/3371a79f5d7b0a0515dfd6cfbed283a5.mp4?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every door, every question, every whisper — it’s all part of you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But do you truly want to remember the truth?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Game Features:</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of puzzles that will test your logic, observation, and imagination.</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An intriguing story with unexpected twists, told through details: there are no long cutscenes here — every element of the world carries a hidden meaning.</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dimensions unlike each other — from 3D worlds where skeletons cannot speak, to 2D worlds with no sound at all, from places where everything has already happened to those where everything is still ahead.</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unusual characters: some will help, some will challenge you, and some will ask questions you might fear to answer.</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A soundtrack that reflects your emotional state.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/63836d625ea0abbe29be35824b5dc977.poster.avif?t=1774345525\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/63836d625ea0abbe29be35824b5dc977.webm?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/63836d625ea0abbe29be35824b5dc977.mp4?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>[/]</ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Who is this game for?</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For those who love:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >atmospheric stories with unexpected twists,</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >puzzles,</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >storytelling through the environment.</p>[/]</ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And at the end, a choice awaits you — one that will decide your fate.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/bb68c29da9e0f0653948af0ef8e166e3.poster.avif?t=1774345525\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/bb68c29da9e0f0653948af0ef8e166e3.webm?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/bb68c29da9e0f0653948af0ef8e166e3.mp4?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>How many worlds are you willing to cross to discover —</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>why you became an empty skull?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>And… were you ever truly someone?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/a5e2030666211c2869abbbe1fee102f7.poster.avif?t=1774345525\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/a5e2030666211c2869abbbe1fee102f7.webm?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/a5e2030666211c2869abbbe1fee102f7.mp4?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/ec8695e1d9b5434be54011110df371bb.poster.avif?t=1774345525\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/ec8695e1d9b5434be54011110df371bb.webm?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/ec8695e1d9b5434be54011110df371bb.mp4?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Sometimes, to remember who you were, you must walk through worlds that never existed.\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You wake up. Around you — emptiness.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You don’t know who you are.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You feel no pain.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You feel no body.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You are nothing but a skull. Empty, like your heart. Oh, right — you don’t have a heart. Yo-ho-ho-ho-ho.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/e9e485ddc4d340fa77a6aa0fe0f7b919.poster.avif?t=1774345525\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/e9e485ddc4d340fa77a6aa0fe0f7b919.webm?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/e9e485ddc4d340fa77a6aa0fe0f7b919.mp4?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Empty Skull</u></strong> is an atmospheric indie adventure puzzle game where you explore mysterious dimensions, strange creatures, fragments of lost memories... and voices that may exist only in your head.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you dive deeper into the worlds between worlds, you begin to realize: you are here for a reason.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/3371a79f5d7b0a0515dfd6cfbed283a5.poster.avif?t=1774345525\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/3371a79f5d7b0a0515dfd6cfbed283a5.webm?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/3371a79f5d7b0a0515dfd6cfbed283a5.mp4?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every door, every question, every whisper — it’s all part of you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But do you truly want to remember the truth?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Game Features:</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of puzzles that will test your logic, observation, and imagination.</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An intriguing story with unexpected twists, told through details: there are no long cutscenes here — every element of the world carries a hidden meaning.</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dimensions unlike each other — from 3D worlds where skeletons cannot speak, to 2D worlds with no sound at all, from places where everything has already happened to those where everything is still ahead.</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unusual characters: some will help, some will challenge you, and some will ask questions you might fear to answer.</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A soundtrack that reflects your emotional state.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/63836d625ea0abbe29be35824b5dc977.poster.avif?t=1774345525\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/63836d625ea0abbe29be35824b5dc977.webm?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/63836d625ea0abbe29be35824b5dc977.mp4?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>[/]</ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Who is this game for?</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>For those who love:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >atmospheric stories with unexpected twists,</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >puzzles,</p>[/][]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >storytelling through the environment.</p>[/]</ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And at the end, a choice awaits you — one that will decide your fate.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/bb68c29da9e0f0653948af0ef8e166e3.poster.avif?t=1774345525\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/bb68c29da9e0f0653948af0ef8e166e3.webm?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/bb68c29da9e0f0653948af0ef8e166e3.mp4?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>How many worlds are you willing to cross to discover —</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>why you became an empty skull?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>And… were you ever truly someone?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/a5e2030666211c2869abbbe1fee102f7.poster.avif?t=1774345525\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/a5e2030666211c2869abbbe1fee102f7.webm?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2772380/extras/a5e2030666211c2869abbbe1fee102f7.mp4?t=1774345525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
